  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to explore efficacy, safety and tolerability of ONO-2952 in
      female subjects with Diarrhea-Predominant Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS-D).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
